{"tid":2347503,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"司機面對揮棍警後退 遭防暴警打至頭破血流 非法集結蒙面罪成 還押候判","createTime":"2020-12-31T05:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T11:40:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7fcbd3b00e16896505f1a3eeb828dbb60acf8076","tid":2347503,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qyHp1RNU48YM-ZIsNDmlzN4bMng=/802x768/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YOA45GUKLYCTJAZRJ5ZSGQN2QE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqyHp1RNU48YM-ZIsNDmlzN4bMng%3D%2F802x768%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYOA45GUKLYCTJAZRJ5ZSGQN2QE.gif&h=1e0cfeea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年11月中環快閃「和你Lunch」期間，警方在交易廣場制服並拘捕多人，有司機遭防暴警打至頭破血流，事後被控襲警、非法集結及身處非法集結時使用蒙面物品三罪，他早前承認襲警罪，否認餘下兩罪。案件審訊後，裁判官張志偉今裁決指，不信被告在警員揮棍驅散下後退是打算離開，而是像「二人對打時作出閃避」，認為被告與他人包圍警方，共同逼使警方「放人」，裁定被告兩罪成立。張官下令索取背景報告，押後案件至明年1月14日求情及判刑，其間被告還押看管。<br />\n<br />\n張官引述片段指，當警員到達平台驅散人群時，被告仍身在人群最前方，與眾人逼向並包圍警員，其目的明顯是要阻止警方帶走被捕人士。張官續指，即使被告在人群投雜物後轉身，也只是轉向其他位置包圍警方，認為他若是打算離開，在警員揮棍驅散下，身體應是背向而非面向警員，即使他有後退亦只是閃避警棍，「如二人對打作出閃避一樣」。<br />\n<br />\n張官認為，被告並非如辯方所言，被警方逼得「退無可退」，而是主動擋格警員的警棍及拉扯其圓盾，其後多次後退及轉身停下，顯然是不願離開現場，目標是對抗警方。張官又指，現場有多人大叫「放人」，被告明顯是響應口號，聯同其他人包圍警方，希望達致讓警方放人的共同目標。<br />\n<br />\n張官認為，被告必然知道該集結有破壞社會安寧的可能性，但仍選擇包圍警員，其間以口罩遮蓋面部，以防他人辨認，最終裁定被告面對的兩罪成立。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/HSNQ2QOFWBAVNM477UF5T27WSI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FHSNQ2QOFWBAVNM477UF5T27WSI%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=56abc9e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FHSNQ2QOFWBAVNM477UF5T27WSI%2F&h=4fd80a6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/HSNQ2QOFWBAVNM477UF5T27WSI/</a>"},{"pid":"2798161c3b31531b2c3853f033c610d9055e025b","tid":2347503,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e2b42b6828b0e165e46236ade4ca10b98ac127","tid":2347503,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6296000046fc3c1cb546d777de477b7a0607059b","tid":2347503,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:51:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1244e06d0856d06da7217d30a74821b2a15d57","tid":2347503,"uid":138964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:52:49.000Z","msg":"襲擊者被打至頭破血流<br />\n被襲者安然無恙"},{"pid":"9654bad3c29ad54121fd3fcc71d70341e715be1b","tid":2347503,"uid":71092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:54:20.000Z","msg":"張官明顯係冇腦"},{"pid":"0ed354caa43ce20693c5150d5722f39420a0da14","tid":2347503,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4129f1b17d3779e4c5b31752f93759563703e7c6","tid":2347503,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as