slike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3764f4848ffd6395dea834b729373047ff03b895","tid":2347503,"uid":33263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係作故事咁作 就可以判"},{"pid":"d69f3b23a917a9f64e8ad2e346682aa120694195","tid":2347503,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:06:01.000Z","msg":"片段顯示在警方警告下，被告面向警方，用右手指著防暴警。辯方指被告打算離開，裁判官質疑若被告欲離開，應該背對警方行走，而非「面向警方向後退」，比喻其動作為「對打中作出閃避」。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官認為被告無視警方警告、不願離開，仍然逗留該處，與包圍警方的人群有共同目的，即要求警方「放人」。人群在場叫口號、叫囂，亦有人向警方投擲雨傘，是帶有威嚇性的擾亂秩序行為，亦激使他人破壞安寧，裁定非法集結罪成。至於身處非法集結時使用蒙面物品罪，片段可見被告一直戴口罩，亦裁定罪名成立。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/11-13-%E4%B8%89%E7%BD%B7-%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6-%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E5%8F%8A%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4-%E5%AE%98-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%96%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E9%A9%85%E6%95%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F11-13-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25BD%25B7-%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%25A9%2585%25E6%2595%25A3%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm2WYsxP5